:: Start
The door isn't locked.

It never was.

Still—
you hesitated.

Something has been softening lately.
Almost sweet.
Almost wasted.

Let's not waste this one.

[[Step inside->LensSelection]]

:: LensSelection
Before we go any further—

What kind of bruise are you here for?

[[A community that stalled->SetLensCommunity]]
[[A creative dream that faded->SetLensCreative]]
[[A strategy that never launched->SetLensStrategic]]
[[An allyship effort that lost its heart->SetLensAllyship]]

[[Learn more: What is this place?->KB_WhatIsThisPlace]]

:: SetLensCommunity
[TOKEN] SET lens=community

Communities don't fracture all at once.
They drift.
And then one day, no one shows up.

Let's catch it before it does.

[[Continue->Signal]]

:: SetLensCreative
[TOKEN] SET lens=creative

Creative work rarely dies loudly.
It fades.
Quietly.
Like paint drying in the dark.

Let's see if there's still heat in it.

[[Continue->Signal]]

:: SetLensStrategic
[TOKEN] SET lens=strategic

Momentum doesn't vanish.
It dissipates.
Because no one claimed it.

Good.

We can work with that.

[[Continue->Signal]]

:: SetLensAllyship
[TOKEN] SET lens=allyship

Allyship loses heart long before it loses language.

You can feel the difference.

Let's name it.

[[Continue->Signal]]

:: Signal
<<if $lens is "creative">>
(If your Twine runtime supports macros, this block is optional. App may ignore.)
<</if>>

There it is.

That low hum under everything.
That thought you keep circling.
That irritation.
That hope.

You don't have to make it impressive.
Just honest.

What's alive right now?

{{INPUT:rawSignal|placeholder=Type what's actually here…}}

[[Continue->Refine]]
[[Learn more: Emotional fuel->KB_EmotionalFuel]]

:: Refine
Good.

Now—
trim it.

Cut the extra words.
Keep the nerve.

One sentence.
Clean.

Bestie.
Don't overthink this.

{{INPUT:refinedSignal|placeholder=Sharpen it to one sentence.}}

When you read it back,
where does it land?

[[In me->QuadrantMe]]
[[In something happening->QuadrantIt]]
[[Between us->QuadrantWe]]
[[In the system itself->QuadrantIts]]

[[Learn more: Why brevity matters->KB_Brevity]]

