:: Claim
If it matters,
it deserves to stand up straight.

No more circling.

Place it in the hall.

[[Publish it->Structure]]
[[Learn more: Public signal->KB_PublicSignal]]

:: Structure
A bruise can rot.

Or it can be used.

Let's see if this one has legs.

[[Continue->Weave]]
[[Learn more: How BARs become action->KB_BarToAction]]

:: Weave
You're not the only one holding something like this.

Signals tend to find each other.

Watch.

[[Continue->Mint]]
[[Learn more: Coordination & the weave->KB_CoordinationWeave]]

:: Mint
There.

Feel that shift?

That's what it feels like when something fragile
becomes usable.

You just minted a vibeulon.

Not metaphorically.

[[Choose your Game Master->ChooseGM]]
[[Learn more: What is a vibeulon?->KB_Vibeulon]]

