:: KB_WhatIsThisPlace
The stacks are older than the app.

Someone tried to explain that once.
It didn't help.

Here's the usable version:

This is a place where signal becomes seed,
seed becomes action,
action becomes capacity.

If you're here,
something in you wants to move.

[[Return->LensSelection]]

:: KB_EmotionalFuel
The stacks smell faintly of citrus and old paper.

You pull a thin volume from the shelf.

The marginalia is dense.

---

Collaborative systems rarely fail because of logistics.

They fail because emotional energy has nowhere to go.

Frustration collapses inward.
Guilt diffuses responsibility.
Shame isolates.
Confusion creates fog.

Emotional Alchemy treats these states as convertible fuel.

When frustration becomes clarity,
capacity increases.

When guilt becomes clean responsibility,
coherence strengthens.

When insight becomes action,
usable value crystallizes.

That's the forge.

---

[[Strengthen this layer (Donate)->Donate_EmotionalFuel]]
[[Return->Signal]]

:: KB_Brevity
You find a torn page, folded twice.

---

Brevity is not aesthetic.

Brevity is respect for attention.

A long signal often contains multiple signals.
That creates confusion.
Confusion creates drift.

One clean sentence can be carried.
Shared.
Acted on.

That's why we cut.

---

[[Strengthen the seed discipline (Donate)->Donate_SeedLibrary]]
[[Return->Refine]]

:: KB_PublicSignal
A stamped note is clipped to the inside cover.

---

Private signal is safe.

Public signal is usable.

The moment a signal enters the hall,
it becomes available for:
collaboration,
refinement,
action.

Public does not mean performative.

Public means shareable.

---

[[Strengthen the hall (Donate)->Donate_SeedLibrary]]
[[Return->Claim]]

:: KB_BarToAction
A diagram has been drawn and erased a dozen times.

---

A BAR is a seed packet.

A quest is a field.

Attaching a BAR to a quest is planting it.

If the quest completes,
capacity is minted with provenance back to the seed.

This is how the system stays honest:
signal must touch reality.

---

[[Strengthen the engine (Donate)->Donate_SeedLibrary]]
[[Return->Structure]]

:: KB_CoordinationWeave
A page has a single line underlined three times:

"Momentum is social."

---

People think coordination is logistics.

It's not.

Coordination is shared attention + clean roles + emotional coherence.

When signals connect,
work becomes lighter.
Not easier—lighter.

This layer trains that.

---

[[Strengthen coordination (Donate)->Donate_Coordination]]
[[Return->Weave]]

:: KB_Vibeulon
You find a small coin taped to a page.
It's warm.

---

A vibeulon is minted capacity.

It marks a transformation:
signal → action → result.

It's a ledger entry you can feel.

Over time, vibeulons make energy visible,
so it can be directed instead of dissipated.

---

[[Strengthen circulation (Donate)->Donate_VibeulonEconomy]]
[[Return->Mint]]

:: KB_SixFaces
A librarian's note, written with a steady hand:

---

The Six Faces are lenses of Game Mastery.

Not personality types.
Not ranks.

Ways of shaping imagination into outcomes.

You'll pick one to walk with you.
Later, you may notice you're learning the others.

That's intentional.

---

[[Strengthen this training (Donate)->Donate_SixFaces]]
[[Return->ChooseGM]]

:: KB_SeedLibrary
The seed library holds ideas that haven't found their field yet.

Someday is a slow death.
The library keeps them alive until they're ready.

---

